'''Gulda Mayir ('''s [[Tutlayt taɛebrit]]  גולדה מאיר ) ( 3 Mayyu 1898 - 8 Dujember 1978 ) d taselwayt n yineɣlafen n [[Israyel]] si [[Meɣres]] 1969 ar 1974 d tamettut tawḥidt yellan deg wadeg-adi . 

tlul-d Gulda mabufitz di temdint n kyib di [[Ukranya]] terzef d twacult-ines ɣer temdint n Milwaki deg uwanek n Wiskunsun deg [[Iwunak Yeddukklen n Temrikt]] aseggas n 1906 . teffeɣ-d si tseddawit n yiselmaden tekcem di ziunizm deg useggas n 1915 terzef abrid nniden ɣer tmurt n [[Falesṭin (Awanek)|Falesṭin]] d urgaz-is Muris Mayersun aseggas n 1921 assmi yemmut deg useggas n 1951 tekkes Sun seg uɣara-ines tuɣal d Mayer 

terzef ɣer temdint n [[Tel Aviv|Tal Abib]] deg 1924 tewwed ɣer lekniset n [[Israyel]] texdem d taneɣlaft n lxedma gar 1949 armi d 1956 d taneɣlaft n berra si 1956 armi d 1966 

assmi yemmut Libi Ickul di [[Furar]] 1969 tuɣal Gulda d taselwayt n yineɣlafen iian wid yugin annecta imi cukken di tezmert-ines ladɣa mi d-yusa nnfaq n Tuber deg 06 [[Tuber]] 1973 imiren teffeɣ si lxedma-s temmut ass n 8 [[Dujember|dujenber]] 1978 temdel di [[Tamdint|temdint]] n [[Uṛacalim]]
